Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Can you imagine that Kamala got up yesterday and tried to pretend she did a good job at the BORDER, when she never even went there, and made it impossible for the great men and women of Border Patrol to properly do their jobs. She let in 14,000 STONE COLD “KILLERS.” I WILL GET THEM OUT, AND FAST!!!
